requirements of a blog.</p>

<h3 id="features">Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Clean, simple and responsive layout.</li>
  <li>Syntax highlighting.</li>
  <li>Sitemap included.</li>
  <li>Google analytics.</li>
  <li>Disqus commenting.</li>
  <li>Share post to facebook and twitter.</li>
  <li>Robots.txt included.</li>
  <li>Custom 404 error page.</li>
</ul>
